Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.12,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}相聚一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.16,0:00:14.98,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}我想打从心里大叫一句 好想快点见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:28.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}我相信总有一天 一定能相遇相知永结连理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.94,0:00:44.01,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}起步走出 希望你能追着我的背影而来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.33,0:00:57.85,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}我孤单一人只为等候你的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.14,0:01:04.95,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}落英缤纷的春日午后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.23,0:01:12.16,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}我将祈祷转为誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.44,0:01:27.05,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}但愿你不会忘记最重要的事 永远闪亮动人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.80,0:01:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝太多的话,开车不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.61,0:01:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了早上酒就会醒的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经订好房间了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.52,0:01:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三…三鹰…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.29,0:01:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果今晚不行的话 明天我也会订房间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.12,0:01:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后天也会订,大后天也会 这样一直订下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:02:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到你对我打开心扉为止 我会一直订下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.41,0:02:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#84 1000%的嫌疑 响子的绯闻之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.19,0:02:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太晚了,响子到底到哪里去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.43,0:02:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我不会让她回家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.97,0:02:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果三鹰是当真的 我在这里等也没有用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.01,0:02:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作,你打算等到什么时候?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.38,0:02:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两个孩子拜托你照顾 我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.28,0:02:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去?你要去哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.68,0:02:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.62,0:02:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.26,0:02:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.79,0:03:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯…伯父
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话想跟响子说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.77,0:03:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员还没回来喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她应该还跟三鹰在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.08,0:03:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是大惊小怪 才九点半而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.31,0:03:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把我女儿拖到半夜 还不让她回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子,等着吧 爸爸马上去救你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点走吧,伯父
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯父?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰,你这么做让我很为难
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这种做法非常粗暴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在开玩笑吧,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.77,0:04:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们房间的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.18,0:04:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来只要…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能找到开启 你心扉的钥匙就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.39,0:04:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说,必须硬把它撬开呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是该怎么说才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暧昧的逃走也解决不了事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰,你听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们出去吹吹夜风吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.14,0:05:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不在的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知不知道 他们还会在其它什么地方吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之,到三鹰可能去的地方 找找看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在这里也没有用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想打个电话回一刻馆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢?你又不是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为大家可能会担心我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又想叫五代出来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.09,0:06:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜对了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会,我才不会做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟这是我跟你的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了,来了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,一刻馆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.99,0:06:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一之濑太太,我还在外面…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊,你慢慢玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.56,0:06:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有什么人 有什么急事找我呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.10,0:07:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,五代呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.14,0:07:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?五代?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道耶,他好像出门去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找他有事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有,没事,那我挂断了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么搞的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.05,0:07:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候,他跑到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定,他是出来找我?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.16,0:07:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他去哪里找了呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有想到什么可能的地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:08:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生,这里不能抽烟啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶心的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶心的地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.47,0:08:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错,有美丽的夜景
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气氛浪漫的酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以看得见海的公园
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此,果然很恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,动作快一点,快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服的风
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会冷?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会,倒是你的酒醒了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.72,0:09:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么做,才能不伤害到我 又能拒绝我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在想这个吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论你怎么做,都很残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.64,0:09:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.85,0:09:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.82,0:09:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这不是道歉 就能解决的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我实在是太随便了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在事情发展到这样之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.22,0:10:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要露出这样的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.40,0:10:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能像这样 也能拥抱住你的心的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.51,0:10:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我会取消的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有办法送你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为看到你的脸,我会觉得很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.95,0:11:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员到底在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.79,0:11:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,天都快亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.19,0:11:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我累了,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想再稍微找一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.14,0:11:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么这么拼命呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说这个,你听了或许会生气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想跟响子结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯父
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.18,0:12:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯父,你怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯父
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.68,0:12:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.47,0:12:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能像这样 也能拥抱住你的心的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代到底到哪里去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯父,不要这么冲动嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.43,0:13:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然一整晚跟男人在夜游
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到她,我一定要给她一巴掌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.77,0:13:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以使用暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且管理员不是那种人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用替她说话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.94,0:13:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个成熟的男女 一整晚都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能什么事都没做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.18,0:13:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且对方是 那个叫三鹰的男人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.09,0:13:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会有什么事!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.74,0:13:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.14,0:14:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会来这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还问我为什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯父,冷静下来慢慢说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,你听到了吧 还亏我们找了她一整晚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子,你实在…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.09,0:14:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,让你担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦,结果,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事…都没发生吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.64,0:14:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.07,0:14:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之,爸爸很相信你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.51,0:14:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,回家睡个觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.09,0:14:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直跟我爸爸在一起吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.87,0:15:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨晚几点回来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概两点左右
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点回来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.65,0:15:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.72,0:15:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害你担心了,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.56,0:15:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.66,0:15:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你到很晚还没回来 我担心你会发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,我说的“什么事” 没有别的意思喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.97,0:15:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,就算有什么事 我也不会在意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,我进去睡一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.98,0:15:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之,平安无事回来就好 平安无事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.52,0:15:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.69,0:16:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,明明就很在意嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是三鹰 她回来的时间又那么晚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两点啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.65,0:17:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.09,0:17:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.62,0:17:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天好温暖喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.79,0:17:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈今天一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.72,0:17:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,我梦见妈妈回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.23,0:17:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊,那个梦一定会成真
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,霞姊知不知道 自己是个母亲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子明明那么相信她 一直在等她回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天感觉好安静喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,因为大家都还在睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.16,0:18:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚好像在四谷的房间 开了宴会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.83,0:18:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长,打起精神来 我妈妈一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.55,0:19:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,对不起,不是的 我不是在说你妈妈的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.62,0:19:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好羡慕太郎的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.35,0:19:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太郎完全相信她 一直在这里等她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.06,0:19:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也曾经很相信你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.49,0:19:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,意思是你现在在怀疑我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又没有这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.63,0:19:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明就是在怀疑我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怀疑你什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.01,0:19:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚,我跟三鹰去饭店…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在酒吧里喝了一点酒 欣赏海景
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:19:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这样而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:20:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所想的事情,都没有发生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.70,0:20:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.74,0:20:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.61,0:20:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.72,0:20:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的口气好像不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.02,0:20:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打从一开始就很相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.76,0:20:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不对?太郎 相信的人才能获得救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人,你明明就在怀疑我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈好慢喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.64,0:20:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.38,0:20:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一她不回来,该怎么办呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.88,0:20:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.15,0:20:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定会回来的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.92,0:20:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.33,0:21:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对喔,霞姊身上带着呼叫器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正在呼叫您拨的号码
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请挂上电话等候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.14,0:21:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太…太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.81,0:21:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎,不要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.05,0:21:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么万一的话 部长会照顾你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.82,0:21:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.42,0:22:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心,妈妈一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.93,0:22:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霞姊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.40,0:22:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.24,0:22:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.38,0:22:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,男孩子怎么哭成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.61,0:22:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候去二楼的?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.48,0:22:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨晚就一直待在二楼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.38,0:22:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不忍心叫醒太郎他们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.82,0:22:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以到隔壁房间去喝酒 结果居然睡着了,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.72,0:22:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,你是管理员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.89,0:22:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你这么照顾我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.93,0:22:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.31,0:22:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.34,0:22:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花子一定也很高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.21,0:23:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎,你很担心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.51,0:23:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然会担心罗,拖到这么晚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.25,0:23:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你相信妈妈对不对 太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.70,0:23:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.13,0:23:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.57,0:23:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙的个性就是这样 你也吃了不少苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.44,0:23:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.34,0:23:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然说什么吃不吃苦的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.71,0:23:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.11,0:23:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟管理员是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.78,0:23:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是房客跟管理员的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.25,0:23:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以,不是那种…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.75,0:23:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.12,0:23:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.64,0:23:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.16,0:23:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代和三鹰教练决斗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.46,0:23:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真蠢,明天明明就要参加 最重要的毕业考了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.50,0:23:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,他们两人 迟早也是要做个了断
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.57,0:24:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.31,0:24:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‘关键时刻! 五代和三鹰宿命的对决’
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.41,0:24:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不会把响子让给你!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.80,0:24:06.80,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.98,0:24:15.71,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}Begin the night Begin your love
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.99,0:24:28.64,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}你该知道这不是擦身而过的恋情 亲吻也是…woo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.17,0:24:46.66,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}你比我想像中冷淡 喜欢一个人独处 沉默不语
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.94,0:24:57.42,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}不要逞强 在这烛火依偎着的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.83,0:25:14.85,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}凝视着你的一切 试着将至今的谎言吹熄
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.55,0:25:22.11,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}Begin the night Begin your love
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.39,0:25:34.50,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}自我陶醉故弄玄虚 对我行不通…woo

